title: Anne, Princess Royal
summary: Anne, Princess Royal KG, KT, GCVO, GCStJ, QSO, CD[2][3][4] (Anne Elizabeth Alice Louise; born 15 August 1950), is the second child and only daughter of Queen Elizabeth II and Prince Philip, Duke of Edinburgh. She is 17th in the line of succession to the British throne[lower-alpha 2] and has been Princess Royal since 1987.[5]
